### ğŸŒŸ Key Announcements

- **The Bloom Engine** is now publicly announced as the first zero-fuel, off-grid harmonic energy engine designed to decentralize power production across the globe.
- Provisional patents are filed. Blueprints are completed. Grant and prototype outreach is underway.
- GoFundMe campaign live: [Support or Contact Us](https://www.gofundme.com/u/root-zero-technologies)

